        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This ornate headgear comes in many different shapes and sizes, though most are elaborately decorated with motifs of the deity whose honor in which it was made. The miter brings you spiritually closer to your deity\u2019s servitors, granting you a +2 item bonus to Religion checks.",
